      "value": "<p>This matching mortar and pestle are made from immaculate duskwood that looks nearly olive in the right light.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> 1 minute (Interact)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You use the <em>mortar of hidden meaning</em> to grind tea leaves (or another suitable substance for making a hot beverage). While grinding the tea leaves, which takes no less than 1 minute, you can speak a message into the mortar. After the leaves are steeped in hot water, the first person who drinks from the resulting brew hears the message whispered in their ear.</p>"
